## Hi there 👋 I'm Emilio Brugés

👨‍🔬 **Biologist (B.Sc.) | Aquatic Ecology | Limnology & Macroinvertebrates | Data Analysis**

I am a biologist with experience in **aquatic biodiversity monitoring**, **macroinvertebrate bioindicators**, and **environmental data analysis**. My work focuses on generating reliable, well-structured information to support environmental assessment, ecosystem health evaluation, and decision-making.

---

### 🔬 Research & Professional Interests
- Limnology and aquatic ecology  
- Aquatic macroinvertebrates as bioindicators  
- Biological Integrity Indices (IBI)  
- Biodiversity monitoring and ecological assessment  
- Environmental data management and analysis  

---

### 🛠️ Technical Skills
- **Statistical software:** RStudio, PAST, SPSS, PRIMER  
- **Data management:** Darwin Core, biodiversity & ICA databases  
- **Data analysis:** Excel (pivot tables, formulas, charts)  
- **Fieldwork:** Sampling design, biological monitoring, GPS, georeferencing  
- **Collaboration tools:** Google Drive, OneDrive, Notion, Trello, Asana  

